<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200911/16da7c878fdc49e9bf9af5eea6300d92.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"> 接着，孟校长携全体教师在国旗下宣誓，铮铮誓言，庄严承诺！昆丽河小学的全体教师必将用实际行动践行，向社会交上一份满意的答卷。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200911/c766380c5f3849d299ae44e573bd2463.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200911/65a1deb7f7d746f8bea6d48a05922cc2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"> 比赛中，参赛教师以生动的事例、真挚的感情、质朴的语言，从不同角度阐述了对教师这一神圣职业的理解和感悟。选手们各具特色，整个比赛精彩纷呈，掌声此起彼伏，充分展现了我校教师爱岗敬业、教书育人、严谨治学、为人师表、与时俱进的精神风貌。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200911/9d19f5b913de4c0f97960ab1c15153c8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200911/140df157cd3048a18871d85cc36e0880.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200911/d55733ab5e444cbc8f54a7580df01b23.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200911/dd693492672142d5b54ad19fa73dd714.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200911/812c4130775c42d0a064fb4c9764763f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200911/d036871bd02b4189b50054b93449cbcb.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200911/b292d0a0a5344d6ca1700ab4dbe7b7c3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200911/f25a0ba91b914414868da97a7891c286.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
